{"tid":241092,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"講早晨有咩新意既講法","createTime":"2017-05-13T01:02:36.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-13T02:46:24.000Z","uid":81247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"18c258a3f81055ba1cdb4a068d50c1507c6981b1","tid":241092,"uid":81247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T01:02:36.000Z","msg":"日日都同佢講早晨<br />\n都不外乎早晨 掘魔零 訓得冧唔冧<br />\n打首早晨歌問下佢<br />\n有時都覺得講到悶<br />\n但又無可能停左唔講<br />\n想問下同另一半講早晨<br />\n有無咩新意可以發揮下 <br />\n一朝早佢就睇得開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"774c2404b8b5eaae9dacf9be1b00f2867f1025f9","tid":241092,"uid":99179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T01:06:23.000Z","msg":"你話「嘩！一早起身見到d咁靚既野」"},{"pid":"9819af4022d162dbe46b55f06c2660cef5846380","tid":241092,"uid":46609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T01:29:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你話「嘩！一早起身見到d咁靚既野」</blockquote><br />\n你話「嘩！屌你老母又落雨？」「唔撚係水浸都黃雨啊？」"},{"pid":"2fe98291f50a0c8fb7245adfece3c484b659df25","tid":241092,"uid":838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T01:32:47.000Z","msg":"起身屌閪喇"},{"pid":"62c34e2d62f5e06954c42b18cfa4d96f0dc3bfd3","tid":241092,"uid":81247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T01:33:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>你話「嘩！一早起身見到d咁靚既野」</blockquote><br />\n你話「嘩！屌你老母又落雨？」「唔撚係水浸都黃雨啊？」</blockquote><br />\n佢通常就會話 唔靚好肥囉<br />\n雖然佢係有小小肥 但成日掛係嘴邊<br />\n成日講佢唔肥唔肥都講到口臭"},{"pid":"99fc858369203a759656502bea20f44e5f91a581","tid":241092,"uid":81247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T01:34:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>起身屌閪喇</blockquote><br />\n真心 想佢起身sweet d見到係開心既回應"},{"pid":"136cb3a01c4cf873047c29db335954b9354214b1","tid":241092,"uid":838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T01:40:48.000Z","msg":"朝朝都講，幾多貨都用盡啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n睇開啲，講句早晨之後諗到咩就講咩開個話題算啦"},{"pid":"b4b5a7